OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine day with light winds and
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine, although
OL,7,Fconditions may become locally hazy
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon. Turning very
OL,9,Fwarm inland, but cooler along the
OL,10,Fcoast as an onshore breeze develops.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAnother warm night for many,
OL,13,Fespecially in urban areas, with cooler
OL,14,Fconditions in rural locations. Dry
OL,15,Fwith light winds and clear skies,
OL,16,Fthough fog may develop in places by
OL,17,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,165,160,301,260,100,100
