PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F164A1783567086
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAnother very warm day, dry and
OL,6,Fpredominantly sunny but the odd
OL,7,Fafternoon shower possible, mostly over
OL,8,Fhills. Cooler along coastal areas,
OL,9,Fwith an onshore breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,12,FCloudier and cooler after a dry and
OL,13,Fbright start on Saturday. Widely
OL,14,Fcloudy on Sunday, with drizzle for
OL,15,Fsome, though brightening up in the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Dry, largely sunny on
OL,17,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
